My 65 Deluxe is not a walk thru but has mount points
for a 2/3 middle seat.  No apparent M code stating it
though.  

I ended up putting a full length seat in there though
because i could not locate a 2/3 for the life of me. 
I had extra mount plates so i welded them in.  now i
can accept both styles although my floor mat is only
for the full length set-up.

Matt

