watchbus(-at-)swcp.com writes:
For what it's worth, I have a '63 15 window.  Here are
the M-Codes:

- 424 - unknown, package?
- 081 - walk-through cab (microbus and deluxe - LHD)
- 114 - six opening side windows (export)
- 130 - microbus deluxe without sliding roof or roof
windows

This Bus will not take a 2/3 middle bench - it lacks
the necessary 
holes 
in both of the middle hold down plates that are welded
to the floor 
(plates are there - no holes).  Plus, the original
rubber mat does not 
have holes for a 2/3 bench's passenger side mounts.

I have had several people try to tell me that
something is wrong with 
my 
Bus, that ALL walk-throughs came with 2/3 middle
benches so you could 
